{"name": "odoo14-addon-sale-promotion-rule", "metadata": {"name": "odoo14-addon-sale-promotion-rule", "version": "14.0.1.0.1", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 4 - Beta", "Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 14.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/sale-workflow", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo"], "summary": "Module to manage promotion rule on sale order", "upload_time": 1686734277}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fsale--workflow-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/sale-workflow\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/sale-workflow/tree/14.0/sale_promotion_rule\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/sale-workflow-14-0/sale-workflow-14-0-sale_promotion_rule\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runbot-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runbot\n    :target: https://runbot.odoo-community.org/runbot/167/14.0\n    ```\n---\n\n# Sale Promotion Rule\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThis module adds the concept of promotion rules that can be applied on the sale\norder.\n\nTwo kinds of rules are implemented:\n: - automatic\n  - coupon\n\nAutomatic rules are applied/recomputed automatically for a sale order when the\nuser clicks on the button \"Apply discount\" in the view form. Depending on the\nrule's criteria more than one automatic rule can be applied to a same sale\norder.\n\nCoupon are special manual rules. Only one coupon can be applied to a\nsale order. This rule takes always precedence over automatic rules.\n\n```{image} https://raw.githubusercontent.com/OCA/sale-workflow/14.0/sale_promotion_rule/sale_promotion_rule/static/description/promotion_rule.png\n:alt: Promotion rules screenshot\n```\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Known issues / Roadmap\n\n- Add gift support. (Only discount offer have been implemented)\n- Improve condition by using custom filter on partner\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/sale-workflow/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us smashing it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/sale-workflow/issues/new?body=module:%20sale_promotion_rule%0Aversion:%2014.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Akretion\n- ACSONE SA/NV\n\n### Contributors\n\n- BEAU S\u00e9bastien \\<<mailto:sebastien.beau@akretion.com>>\n- Beno\u00eet GUILLOT \\<<mailto:benoit.guillot@akretion.com>>\n- Laurent Mignon \\<<mailto:laurent.mignon@acsone.eu>>\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/sale-workflow](https://github.com/OCA/sale-workflow/tree/14.0/sale_promotion_rule) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.sale_promotion_rule.models", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.sale_promotion_rule.models.sale_order", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.sale_promotion_rule.models..sale_order", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.sale_promotion_rule.models.sale_order_line", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.sale_promotion_rule.models..sale_order_line", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.sale_promotion_rule.models.sale_promotion_rule", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.sale_promotion_rule.models..sale_promotion_rule", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.sale_promotion_rule.models.sale_order_line", "documentation": ["Copyright 2017 Akretion (http://www.akretion.com).", "@author Beno\u00eet GUILLOT <benoit.guillot@akretion.com>", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.sale_promotion_rule.models.sale_order_line.SaleOrderLine", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [{"name": "odoo.addons.sale_promotion_rule.models.sale_order_line.SaleOrderLine._compute_has_promotion_rules", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.sale_promotion_rule.models.sale_order_line.SaleOrderLine._compute_applied_promotion_rule_ids", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.sale_promotion_rule.models.sale_order_line.SaleOrderLine._inherit", "type": nul